New Delhi, the 19th October, 1956.
The undersigned is directed to circulate a copy of
the Order dated the 16th October, 1956, made by the Prime
Minister regarding the allocation of work consequent upon
the division of the Ministry of Food & Agriculture into two
separate Ministries of Food and of Agriculture.

ORDER
On the division of the Ministry of Food &
Agriculture into two separate Ministries, namely, a
Ministry of Food and a Ministry of Agriculture, the
following allocation of work is orderedi-
1. Shri A.P. Jain will hold charge of both
the Ministries of Food and of Agriculture.
2. Dr. Panjabrao S. Deshmukh, Minister of
Agriculture, will be attached to the
Ministry of Agriculture.
RAJPUT
250 copies.
-197
3. Shri M.V. Krishnappa, at present Deputy
Minister of Food and Agriculture, will
be attached to the Ministry of Food and
designated as Deputy Minister of Food,
Sd/- J. Nehru
